==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Jaal goat
<hw>Jaal" goat`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A species of
wild goat (<spn>Capra Nubiana</spn>) found in the mountains of
Abyssinia, Upper Egypt, and Arabia; -- called also
<altname>beden</altname>, and <altname>jaela</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

